{"word":"Laban","slug":"laban","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Laban</b> <a href=\"#/H3837\">H3837</a> <br/> Son of Bethuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=5'>Gen 28:5</a><br/> Brother of Rebekah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=23'>Gen 22:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=15'>Gen 24:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=29'>Gen 24:29</a><br/> Receives the servant of Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=33'>Gen 24:33</a><br/> Receives Jacob, and gives him his daughters in marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=30'>Gen 29:30</a><br/> Jacob becomes his servant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=20'>Gen 29:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=27'>Gen 29:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=43'>Gen 30:43</a><br/> Outwitted by Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=43'>Gen 30:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=21'>Gen 31:21</a><br/> Pursues Jacob, overtakes him at Mount Gilead, and covenants with him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=55'>Gen 31:55</a>"}]}